{"tid":101110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]今日係到教大家一招改圖大絕","createTime":"2017-01-30T14:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T17:01:27.000Z","uid":1458,"like":12,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb411a206568ef00ea62c502a17a018ee855aeb","tid":101110,"uid":1458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"大家好， 今日想教大家一個改圖既大技<br />\n我會叫佢做 <strong>檢查天素大法</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做法好簡單 mac 同window都可以做到<br />\n今日請左林鄭同大家做示範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">正式開始</span><br />\n首先係chrome開一個你想改既網頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B82Bxv4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB82Bxv4.jpg&h=b98593c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後就係highlight你想改既字，之後右鍵再㩒檢查，window應該會見到檢查元素<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/221249_a879522779d1962387ecece0640d3a52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F221249_a879522779d1962387ecece0640d3a52.jpg&h=6c63b383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n㩒入去之後應該會彈左一個網頁html碼既表出黎，右click自動highlight左嗰行.㩒Edit as html<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3523q65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3523q65.jpg&h=584804ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下一步就係將原本嗰句改為你想要既字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/221511_1148b79520bfcd4e84711c30ae0aca23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F221511_1148b79520bfcd4e84711c30ae0aca23.jpg&h=16a4ab65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n改完㩒一下個網就會發生可怕既事情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Ke6RLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Ke6RLJ.jpg&h=957919bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上呢招已經可以改任何網頁啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">圖都可以改架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n首先求其係網上面揾一張圖 一樣做法 右鍵檢查edit as html.但今次係將src後面既網址copy<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/223400_a03759ac638e3fcfc9b8597dcba6d217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F223400_a03759ac638e3fcfc9b8597dcba6d217.jpg&h=4906c452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返到改緊嗰頁做同樣動作用copy左既取代原本嗰個<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/30/223527_1377c104015f50f76154da2e06f50dce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2F223527_1377c104015f50f76154da2e06f50dce.jpg&h=88995f81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就大功告成啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>改圖前</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B82Bxv4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB82Bxv4.jpg&h=b98593c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>改圖後</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4iddoi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4iddoi5.jpg&h=b8fa2817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想還原重新整理個網就搞掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ed5a544959313c7f8b3f85fd1af0ad9a2b124d","tid":101110,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f405864705122b6864154fb3b2308ccd57a0faa","tid":101110,"uid":35173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69778be03fdca488cce763c2c0b327030a820bca","tid":101110,"uid":1458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知有冇人教過呢招呢"},{"pid":"8c8cff3fff105c4d622f4be501970e3f823b419c","tid":101110,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:44:18.000Z","msg":"改完無得upload 改黎做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989584a3bb69a9e387d21f93c818ca25c56293c7","tid":101110,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32994789f57c10ab63d865b2d7ec87cfb047fd55","tid":101110,"uid":1458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>改完無得upload 改黎做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚用黎改同女神relationship <img s